{"tid":1264233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長期戰做三樣野: 杯葛大台, 出戰區選, 覺醒人民","createTime":"2019-06-28T15:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T05:18:43.000Z","uid":196536,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd7945d6d28efac905e9307e042644fd692e9aa","tid":1264233,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"杯葛大台:<br />\n好多巴打講左, 即係取締mytvsuper, 盡量係屋企唔睇大台, 於不干擾採訪下對TVB作出不合作運動, 同要求食肆轉台<br />\n<br />\n出戰區選:<br />\n作為公民, 我地需要增加區選的投入度, 有人出人, 冇人出錢(主要係個保証金), 十八區既然有TG, 可以試行下, 首要目標係打果D自動當選選區<br />\n<br />\n覺醒人民:<br />\n最重要一環, 深藍/廢老/無知師奶/廢青我地都唔可以放過, 仲要留意上次616既首行族, 要盡量將呢200萬人化為選票, 呢條惡法係說服佢地既契機, 再帶出呢個狼虎正苦推此惡法ge終極動機.<br />\n<br />\n既然連正苦都棄我城不顧, 那它就由我們每人來守護."},{"pid":"e1695b50f636f68a690b69e18203113b5e6ced56","tid":1264233,"uid":197540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"原來你講緊呢個大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ac724120f920c7b50cbcbfe51c1577382ec49f","tid":1264233,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1695b50f636f68a690b69e18203113b5e6ced56","tid":1264233,"uid":197540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"原來你講緊呢個大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次冇大台呀嘛我諗住"},{"pid":"9134aeabb29157780e2c94493d7831d7a32da6fd","tid":1264233,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1695b50f636f68a690b69e18203113b5e6ced56","tid":1264233,"uid":197540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"